 -45c to +75c StorageFeatures:640×480 MicroIR Thermal Sensor60hz Super Fast ImageDCE: Digital Contrast Enhance35% More MagnificationEdge Detection Mode40% Longer Battery LifeIncreased Clip-On CapabilitySharper Image QualityDigital Brightness ControlVideo OutputComes with: IR Hunter MKII Sight, Larue Tactical Weapon Mount, Eyeguard, Tactical Soft Case, Lanyard, Lens Cap, Operator’s Manual QRG Guide and batteries. Available with a 19MM or 35MM lens. All night vision devices in part or whole are strictly regulated by the US Department of State in accordance with the guidelines in the International Traffic in Arms (ITAR) per title 22, Code of Federal Regulations (CFR), Parts 120-130. Therefore, if you are outside the United States, INCLUDING Canada, you must obtain an export license. MOD Armory does not export out of the United States!Additional InformationIR HUnter MKII19MM, 35MMReviewsThere are no reviews yet.Only logged in customers who have purchased this product may leave a review.  Recent Images   Related Products    Mystery Ranch AOR2 RECCE Field ...$699.99  Add to cart   MORP MEDICAL ORGANIZER RESCUE PACK$165.00  Add to cart   Sons Trauma Kit Ultra Thin ...$35.00  Add to cart  Sale!  32430 Gun Cleaning Kit for M4/...$33.68 $30.00  Add to cart   M240 Buttstock and buffer assemblyFrom $150.00  Select options   Factory Glock .40 cal Dark Earth ...$100.00  Add to cart   Surefire EP330 Boom Mic with ...$300.00  Add to cart  Sale!  Leupold FX-II Scout 2.5x28mm ...$324.99 $298.99  Add to cart   MRT Leather M24 Rifle Sling$35.00  Select options   aiShell Air iPad Case for ...$220.00  Add to cart   aiShell iPad Case Mini+ for ...$199.99  Add to cart   PVS-14 Housing Parts KitFrom $849.00  Select options                          



