ProductsYou are here: Home / Products / Metal Detectors / Metal Detectors by Category / Water / Land Metal Detectors / Garrett Sea Hunter Mark II Underwater Metal Detector +8″ PROformance Search Coil



 

 


Financing Available 


Garrett Sea Hunter Mark II Underwater Metal Detector +8″ PROformance Search CoilMSRP: $749.95 $637.45

Garrett Sea Hunter Mark II Underwater Metal Detector with 8″ PROformance Submersible Search Coil, Submersible Headphones, Belt pouch, Batteries and a One-Year Limited Parts/Labor Warranty.
The Sea Hunter Mark II underwater detector features Circuit type Pulse Induction technology, Adjustable Audio Threshold, User-adjustable Discrimination, Discrete Trash Elimination and All Metal Deep Seeking Mode with Full Range PI discrimination.
This underwater metal detector is ideal for Beaches, Lakes, Oceans, and all Waterways. The Sea Hunter Mark II is an advanced microprocessor-driven instrument that is lightweight, highly durable and easy to use.

In stock




Add to cart


